channel.title: Anyone Need a Developer?
channel.description:
Hello, So long story shot, I used to make Minecraft plugins and sell them.
Made a Decent Amount with that, Now i have a Job doing web development for businesses with 500 or less employees.

Can I code ? Of course lmao

Anyways, If you want a serious Dev, just let me know.
Oh yea i forgot, I dont want any proceeds from the Donations
So pm me on the forums or msg me on twitter at www.twitter.com/driftay
